            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-10 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-6xl"><%= dgettext("home", "Messaging made simple for small businesses.") %></h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8"><%= dgettext("home", "Wariva is a delightfully simple async communication platform. It's fast, free, and easy to use. With all the features you need to have a successful community. It's also extremely extensible, allowing for ultimate customizability.") %></p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-x-6">
        <a href="/register" class="rounded-md bg-amber-600 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-amber-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-amber-600"><%= dgettext("home", "Get started") %></a>
        <a href="#features" class="text-base font-semibold leading-7"><%= dgettext("home", "Learn more") %> <span aria-hidden="true">â†’</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 flex max-w-2xl sm:mt-24 lg:ml-10 lg:mt-0 lg:mr-0 lg:max-w-none lg:flex-none xl:ml-32">
